description: Performs 10 mc runs at integer undersampling point in the grid of half-width 0.1 around predicted undersampling point, with blocksoft denoiser. Sparsity varies from 0.02 to 0.98 in interval of 0.02. Number of blocks varies in [100, 200, 300, 400, 500] and block size varies in [20]. var(resid) used to estimate the noise var at each iteration.
